# Branding & Design System

## Source of Truth

**ALWAYS refer to `docs/branding-guide.html` for the exact color codes, font families, and component styles.**

## Core Design Rules

### Pixel Art Theme
- **NO smooth gradients or rounded corners** (unless pixelated)
- **ALL images must use the `.pixel-art` utility class** (image-rendering: pixelated)
- **Borders:** Use chunky 4px solid borders

### Color Palette (Dark Mode)
- **Background:** `#2D1B4E` (Deep Indigo) - `var(--bg-dark)`
- **Card Background:** `#433D60` - `var(--card-bg)`
- **Primary Action:** `#FF70A6` (Bubblegum Pink) - `var(--primary)`
- **Secondary Action:** `#70D6FF` (Electric Blue) - `var(--secondary)`
- **Accent/Badge:** `#E9FF70` (Neon Lime) - `var(--accent)`
- **Gold/Currency:** `#FFD670` - `var(--gold)`

### Typography
- **Headings:** `'Press Start 2P'` (Use sparingly for big titles)
- **Body:** `'VT323'` (Terminal style, readable)

## UI Components

### Buttons

**CRITICAL:** All buttons MUST use the global button classes defined in `shop/assets/css/style.css`.

**Base Class:** `.pixel-btn`
- 4px solid borders
- Light top/left border: `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3)`
- Dark bottom/right border: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)`
- Active state: `translateY(4px)`, `border-width: 2px`
- Hover: `brightness(1.1)`

**Color Variants:**
- `.pixel-btn-primary` - Primary actions (Pink background, white text)
- `.pixel-btn-secondary` - Secondary actions (Blue background, black text)
- `.pixel-btn-accent` - Accent actions (Lime background, black text)
- `.pixel-btn-gold` - Currency/rare actions (Gold background, black text)
- `.pixel-btn-danger` - Destructive actions (Red background, white text)
- `.pixel-btn-disabled` - Disabled state (Gray background, gray text)

**Usage:**
```html
<!-- ‚úÖ CORRECT -->
<button class="pixel-btn pixel-btn-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm">BUY</button>
<button class="pixel-btn pixel-btn-secondary px-4 py-2 text-sm">CANCEL</button>
<button class="pixel-btn pixel-btn-danger px-4 py-2 text-sm">DELETE</button>

<!-- ‚ùå WRONG - Don't use inline bg-* classes with pixel-btn -->
<button class="pixel-btn bg-primary text-white">BUY</button>
```

**Legacy Support:** `.pixel-btn-3d` is an alias for `.pixel-btn` but prefer `.pixel-btn` for new code.

### Item Cards

**CRITICAL:** All item cards MUST use the `.item-card` class.

**Required Classes:**
- `.item-card` - Base class (includes border-4 border-primary, hover:scale-105)
- Background: `var(--bg-dark)` (#2D1B4E)
- Border: `4px solid var(--primary)` (#FF70A6)
- Hover effect: `scale(1.05)` transition
- Padding: `1rem`
- Position: `relative` (for badges)

**Usage:**
```html
<!-- ‚úÖ CORRECT -->
<div class="item-card">
    <img src="..." class="pixel-art" alt="Item">
    <h3 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Press_Start_2P']">Item Name</h3>
    <p class="text-gold text-xl">üí∞ 100</p>
</div>

<!-- ‚ùå WRONG - Missing hover effect and proper border -->
<div class="bg-[#2D1B4E] border-2">...</div>
```

**Admin Item Cards:** Use `.item-card.admin-item-card` to disable hover (admin cards are not clickable).

### Cards

**Base Card:** `.pixel-card`
- Background: `var(--card-bg)` (#433D60)
- Border: `4px solid #000`
- Box-shadow: `8px 8px 0 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)`
- Padding: `1.5rem`

### Images

**CRITICAL:** ALL images MUST have the `.pixel-art` class to prevent blurring.

```html
<!-- ‚úÖ CORRECT -->
<img src="..." class="pixel-art" alt="Sprite">

<!-- ‚ùå WRONG - Image will be blurred -->
<img src="..." alt="Sprite">
```

**CSS Rule (MUST be in style.css):**
```css
.pixel-art {
    image-rendering: pixelated;       /* Chrome/Safari */
    image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges; /* Firefox */
    image-rendering: crisp-edges;     /* Standard */
}
```

## Layout Guidelines

### Headers
- Use `flex items-center justify-between gap-4` for header layouts
- Add `flex-wrap` for responsive behavior
- Use `flex-shrink-0` on button groups to prevent squishing
- Buttons should be grouped in a container: `<div class="flex gap-3 items-center">`

### Spacing
- Use consistent gaps: `gap-3` for button groups, `gap-4` for header elements
- Padding: `px-4 py-2` for standard buttons, `px-3 py-1` for small buttons

## The "Vibe" Checklist

‚úÖ **Dark Mode Default:** Easy on the eyes, makes neon colors pop
‚úÖ **Chunky Borders:** Everything has a 2px-4px solid border
‚úÖ **No Smoothing:** All images use `image-rendering: pixelated`
‚úÖ **Juicy Feedback:** Buttons press down, hover states lift up
‚úÖ **Kawaii Copy:** Use "Opps!" instead of "Error", "Yay!" instead of "Success"

## Common Mistakes to Avoid

‚ùå **Don't mix Tailwind bg-* classes with pixel-btn** - Use the color variant classes instead
‚ùå **Don't forget .pixel-art on images** - Images will blur without it
‚ùå **Don't use border-2 on item cards** - Must be border-4 border-primary
‚ùå **Don't forget hover effects on item cards** - Must have hover:scale-105
‚ùå **Don't use rounded corners** - Pixel art theme requires sharp edges

